{"tid":2095123,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"城大研新晶片提升網速 一秒內下載千套高清電影","createTime":"2020-07-05T08:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T13:52:47.000Z","uid":225931,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"69d4c790a7378f80396bb77ac629d49a018b465f","tid":2095123,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2685000/2687013/Photo_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2685000%2F2687013%2FPhoto_02_600.jpg&h=e821fcc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數碼年代加上疫情衝擊，互聯網速度對工作、社交及娛樂都日漸重要。城大物理學系副教授朱世德參與的國際團隊研發出新型晶片，可以大幅提升互聯網速度至歷來最快，[img]下載1,000部高清電影亦需時少於一秒[/img]。<br />\n<br />\n是次研究證明「微梳」的功能，微梳是基於微環諧振器的光頻率反應，能進行超高光學數據傳輸。微環諧振器是一個小巧的集成晶片，可提供所有波長並替代許多並行激光。在澳洲斯威本理工大學的實地測試中，研究員使用一種功能強大的微梳，名為「光孤子晶體」，結果網速達到每秒44.2兆位元，頻譜效率也達到創紀錄的每秒10.4位元/赫茲，比現有紀錄高3.7倍。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653cd268fd424bfe1e2998d5bf72786c73610e0d","tid":2095123,"uid":346084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"吾城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fe7266dc93c69059bca2ae0d765b4c79ae6967","tid":2095123,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"要多謝朱教授偉大的發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73525dd994ff94537b4f669b2a4a1931b0bdb6c2","tid":2095123,"uid":132587,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"下載1,000部<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">AV</span>亦需時少於一秒"},{"pid":"27fd4d10a4835c97e0ddc19b50f8e6a9ad88b124","tid":2095123,"uid":133823,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVH28Gj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg